text: Colobothea lineatocollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1865. It is known from French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Colobothea lineatocollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1865
title: Colobothea lineatocollis
